 remover into the filter using the small port holes.
 2 mL of liquid will fill the filter to about the mid way between the top
 of the puler board capacitors and the fill port.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Swirl for a few seconds then drain the flux remover into a waste beaker.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Repeat until all flux is removed as indicated by drained flux remover running
 clear.
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Wipe down liquid around the filter 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
